OL,4,Cglittering Michelin guide ceremony
OL,6,FHe has presided over Moor Hall, in a
OL,7,Fstunning landscaped estate in the
OL,8,Fvillage of Aughton, near Ormskirk in
OL,9,FLancashire, for the past eight years.
OL,11,FMark Birchall spoke to Granada Reports
OL,12,FCorrespondent Victoria Grimes after
OL,13,Fthe ceremony.
