OL,3,CEmotional night for chefs at
OL,4,Cglittering Michelin guide ceremony
OL,6,FAccepting the coveted chef jacket
OL,7,Fembroidered with three Michelin stars,
OL,8,Fa visibly overcome Birchall said: "You
OL,9,Fdream about this moment and how you
OL,10,Fwould feel, but the emotion is
OL,11,Fincredible. One of the best feelings
OL,12,Fever in my life was getting the first
OL,13,Fstar, but this is just incredible."
OL,15,FHe was surrounded on stage by the
OL,16,Fother UK chefs who hold three stars,
OL,17,Fincluding Simon Rogan of L'Enclume in
OL,18,FCartmell and Clare Smyth of Core in
OL,19,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
