OL,3,CEmotional night for chefs at
OL,4,Cglittering Michelin guide ceremony
OL,6,FMichelin inspectors summed up the
OL,7,Fachievements of Mark after the event.
OL,8,FThey wrote: "At Moor Hall, Chef Mark
OL,9,FBirchall and his team have continued
OL,10,Fto hone their craft and have now
OL,11,Fachieved new levels of excellence.
OL,13,FThe ingredients, many from the kitchen
OL,14,Fgarden, are outstanding; the chefs'
OL,15,Fculinary technique is hugely
OL,16,Fimpressive; and the judgement of
OL,17,Fflavours, of when to prioritise
OL,18,Fsimplicity and when to add complexity,
OL,19,Fis exemplary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
