OL,3,CEmotional night for chefs at
OL,4,Cglittering Michelin guide ceremony
OL,6,FSpeaking to Granada Reports after the
OL,7,Fceremony Birchall said: "It was a big
OL,8,Fsurprise and just amazing to hear our
OL,9,Frestaurant get called out!
OL,11,F'We started out eight years ago with
OL,12,Fan outrageous ambition to create a
OL,13,Fworld class dining destination in the
OL,14,Fnorth of England. We were awarded our
OL,15,Ffirst star a few months after we
OL,16,Fopened in 2017, then our second just
OL,17,Fthe year later, now ` just 8 years
OL,18,Ffrom the day we opened our doors, we
OL,19,Fare awarded 3 stars.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
