OL,3,CEmotional night for chefs at
OL,4,Cglittering Michelin guide ceremony
OL,6,FIs the Lancashire village of Aughton
OL,7,Fbecoming the food capital of the UK?
OL,9,FElsewhere at the awards there were 22
OL,10,Fnew One Michelin Star restaurants
OL,11,Fannounced - including Manchester's
OL,12,FSkof.
OL,14,FSkof received the award - less than a
OL,15,Fyear after opening in the city centre.
OL,16,FThe restaurant is presided over by
OL,17,Fformer L'Enclume chef Tom Barnes.
OL,19,FTom was in Glasgow alongside the cream
OL,20,Fof the culinary world.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
