OL,3,CEmotional night for chefs at
OL,4,Cglittering Michelin guide ceremony
OL,6,FBased in an historic former drapery in
OL,7,Fthe Hanover Building on Federation
OL,8,FStreet in the city centre, Skof is the
OL,9,Fbrainchild of chef Barnes.
OL,11,FIt's now become the second Manchester
OL,12,Frestaurant to hold a Michelin Star,
OL,13,Falongside Mana in Ancoats.
OL,15,FSpeaking after the ceremony, Barnes
OL,16,Fsaid: "I'm so happy - everyone in the
OL,17,Fteam has worked so hard for this.
OL,18,FManchester has really welcomed us and
OL,19,FI'm buzzing to be able to bring this
OL,20,Fstar back to them!'
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
