OL,3,CEmotional night for chefs at
OL,4,Cglittering Michelin guide ceremony
OL,6,FIt follows disappointment for
OL,7,FManchester after last year's ceremony,
OL,8,Fwhere its restaurants failed to be
OL,9,Fhonoured, despite the awards ceremony
OL,10,Fbeing held in the city centre.
OL,12,FGwendal Poullennec, International
OL,13,FDirector of The Michelin Guides, said:
OL,14,F"I am so thrilled to see that our
OL,15,FGreat Britain & Ireland Guide has had
OL,16,Fsuch a strong year yet again. Despite
OL,17,Fthe challenges they face, chefs and
OL,18,Frestaurateurs have shown us that their
OL,19,Ftalent, commitment and ingenuity know
OL,20,Fno bounds.
